transportation of waste out of county; residential services to pick up trash recycling materials and household hazardous waste; composting; public education on solid waste; Pratt Recycling of Conyers Georgia at 5:30 p.m. May 19: processing of recycling materials and transporting that out of the county.

The committee also will meet again to discuss all the proposals at 5:30 p.m. May 26.

